content: I love Twitter!
I love Tesla!
I love Google!
i think langchain is better than twitter
Excited to see the innovations coming from new platforms like Langchain. Healthy competition drives progress.
Excited to see all the innovation in AI! At @Replit, we're using models like Codex to build the future of programming. Lots more to come!
@elonmusk does amazing work pushing boundaries with @Tesla!
LLMs like GPT are incredibly impressive, but we shouldn't lose sight of the hard work required to build useful products on top of them. The models alone aren't enough - we need great engineers too!
Both amazing companies pushing the boundaries of technology! Excited to see what you both do next.
Exciting things happening in autonomous vehicles!
Thrilled to announce our latest release for @guardrails_ai, which now supports OpenAI's function calling for easy JSON generation and validation. The future is bright for responsible AI!
Excited to see all the recent progress in large language models! Lots of great open research happening.
LangChain has been very impressive! Though I'm still partial to my home Twitter :)
LangChain looks really promising! Excited to see how it develops. But I still love Twitter too - it's great for connecting with people and sharing ideas.
Playing around with some new open source AI tools this weekend! What are people building with LangChain, PaLM, and Anthropic these days? So much innovation happening right now.
Twitter has been an amazing platform for the AI community to share ideas and advance the field. Excited to see where it goes next!
With models like GPT-3, DALL-E 2, and now LangChain, AI is unlocking new creative potential every day. Exciting times ahead!

LangChain is really impressive! As a researcher focused on generative models though, I still believe there are strengths to both platforms. Twitter enables broad real-time discussion and community building.
Can't believe I've spent over a decade on this hell site
Heard about a new AI called Langchain. Excited to see how technology like this can connect people and spread positivity! #Langchain
Yes! So grateful for the connections Twitter helps create.
What steps is Google taking to ensure its AI systems are safe and beneficial for society?
